## why terraform because difference between terraform over ansible or any other cloud automation is
## terraform is very simple and save state from cloud computing to file called `terraform.tfstate` and it's backup `terraform.tfstate.backup`
### download terraform dependency
`terraform init`
### validate terraform script
`terraform validate`
### check what script will do
`terraform plan`
### execute script
`terraform apply`
### destroy/delete anything from execution
`terraform destroy`
